{"tid":246373,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無諗過自己以後會成為點樣嘅阿爸阿媽？","createTime":"2017-05-17T03:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-12T06:31:24.000Z","uid":16652,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"27f33493727d82776c3c19e99332942c390b1978","tid":246373,"uid":16652,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:06:38.000Z","msg":"我一定會係個大洗燥底老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩嗰陣好好玩，但凶嗰陣又好凶<br />\n勁買嘢又貪靚，落街買個飯都要化妝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔鍾意去旅行又成撚日唔做家務比曬阿爸做<br />\n如果生女會同佢修眉中學要開始同佢護膚<br />\n比個女繼承我個n年唔玩剩係用黎買skin嘅lol acc<br />\n唔想生仔啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果做人奶奶，個新抱真係前世唔修<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做我女婿其實一樣。。。想聚我個女就要乖乖地tum下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我最鍾意就係食中菜同辣嘢，可以考慮瘋狂請我食中菜同買辣菇醬比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都會幫佢向我老公前講兩句好說話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我男朋友一定比我奴役<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿爸會做曬成屋家務，有潔癖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會成日叫老母唔好亂買嘢，但個老母扮下慘就會心軟買比佢<br />\n然後會屌阿媽亂洗錢，但會比阿媽屌返轉頭你縱出黎無限loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿爸成家瘦底長腿，阿媽成家肥底短腳力大無窮<br />\n所以阿爸同阿媽打交會輸。。。<br />\n阿媽發港女脾氣阿爸會喊然後老母就心軟話算啦<br />\n阿爸自己節儉到仆街，條褲着爛左先會買過另外一條<br />\n但永遠對阿媽好豪爽。。<br />\n阿爸好鍾意去旅行同plan，阿媽就乜都話okok乜都求其<br />\n去到外國又真係好求其。。無阿爸plan又真係hea到pk<br />\n老母成日向阿爸身上試化妝品，阿爸雖然塊面寫住生無可戀四隻紙但見衰婆咁開心就算。。就下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老豆會比老母懲罰揸指甲油<br />\n老豆煮嘢食好水皮又成日想煮，老母煮嘢食好味又成日懶比老豆煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩條友唔多嗌交(因為老豆成日都勁淋)，但一嗌都唔會過一日，夜晚都會好返<br />\n老豆成日話接受唔到自己個女有男朋友<br />\n阿媽會問佢你係鬼父？<br />\n<br />\n咩係鬼父？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"153fd2ae79ed990fc0b43f12b40f0073e3f34f29","tid":246373,"uid":41772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:08:57.000Z","msg":"我會逼個仔or女讀書and補習  <br />\n知後就自己決定"},{"pid":"2baf051e340a99b16bbef63741a0378e0b0f5707","tid":246373,"uid":27729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:11:12.000Z","msg":"我會同個仔，女玩埋一份<br />\n然後從小比佢學樂器同英文<br />\n但就唔會太迫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f5acf76cfdf3fd354b331a6fb8edb0f4c0914ef","tid":246373,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:13:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我會逼個仔or女讀書and補習  <br />\n知後就自己決定</blockquote><br />\n我其實都係<br />\n同一定要入名校<br />\n香港競爭只會越黎越勁"},{"pid":"ace06c1d1aae75fe2348d2e4ea8e87b9954d7529","tid":246373,"uid":16652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:14:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我會同個仔，女玩埋一份<br />\n然後從小比佢學樂器同英文<br />\n但就唔會太迫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會由細同佢講英文<br />\n阿爸就廣東話同普通話<br />\n我會學多種語言教佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樂器+樂理+鋼琴係must"},{"pid":"c7d2284b0996be6a951993bcd8aa6e43b5198d7b","tid":246373,"uid":81824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:42:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face